Package org.emoncms.http

Class HttpInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.emoncms.http.HttpInput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Input
    public class HttpInput
extends java.lang.Object
implements Input
    The HttpInput implementation provides the Emoncms interface for HTTP input requests. Inputs hold all their configuration fields in memory, but may be cleared to only hold their ID, node and name by calling clear(). Input methods only need those variables to maintain their functionality and other resources may be released to save memory. Current values for all fields can be retrieved by calling load().
